@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

@{MS "Introduction"}

ParKeyboard is a hard and software solution to connect a second keyboard by using the parallel port.@{par}

I wrote this tool for testing @{"my" link "Author"} @{"MMKeyboard" link "OtherPRGs"} hardware.
Before using the ParKeyboard interface it was required to bridge my internal interface to get an original Amiga
keyboard connector. If something went wrong I had to do tricky things to get my keyboard working
again. Thanks to ParKeyboard my Amiga owns a second keyboard connector to testing purpose.@{par}


@endnode
@node "Systemrequirements" "Systemrequirements"

@{MS "System requirements"}

ParKeyboard (should work) works on all Amigas with OS 2.0 or higher.@{par}

Also required is an Amiga with a free internal parallel port! (-8

