@node "Buglist" "Buglist"

@{MS "Buglist"}

The reset handler isn't working by using this keyboard connector! The reason is simple! There is no
way to activate the external reset handler!@{par}

The keyboard repeat isn't working. The reason is: I didn't programmed it. (-8@{par}

Some keyboards (e.G. A500, A1000 and some A2000) aren't reseting the system. ParKeyboard is using
the ResetWarning to detect a reset. For most keyboards and for the @{"MMKeyboard" link "OtherPRGS"}
interface there is no problem with the reset. If there is a problem you may use a hotkey tool and
start a tools like Reboot.

